Hitler did not burn art. He stole it and preserved it.

Hitler didn't get into art school because his art was too traditional and the style that was in at the time was surrealist and modern. Since he didn't get into art school because of this, he really despised everything that wasn't traditional. After he came to power he opened a traveling museum called Entarterte Kunst which means "degenerate art". The purpose of the museum was solely to mock everything he considered ugly, jewish, communist or was made by an enemy of the state.  it was a big hit in Germany!
